title: Episode 24 w/ Cormega and Cory Gunz
itunes:title: Episode 24 w/ Cormega and Cory Gunz
description:
N.O.R.E. and DJ EFN are the Drink Champs. In this bonus episode the guys sit with Cormega and Cory Gunz after a recent show in Miami. The guys talk about Cormega's career, Queensbridge history, the Firm, lyricism in hip hop and a lot more. --- Support this podcast: https://anchor.fm/drinkchamps/support
